00:00:13.100 --> 00:00:15.870
And also because it is a math
card trick, it will involve a

00:00:15.870 --> 00:00:18.400
lot of tedious counting.

00:00:18.400 --> 00:00:19.370
So this is how this
is going to work.

00:00:19.370 --> 00:00:21.580
I have a normal deck
of cards, there are

00:00:21.580 --> 00:00:22.970
