the first time,

00:08:14.610 --> 00:08:15.630
so I doubted myself.

00:08:15.630 --> 00:08:17.620
But you know what, it probably
is that number.

00:08:17.620 --> 00:08:19.510
Then you count them off again,
and the important thing is

00:08:19.510 --> 00:08:22.520
this time you count off that
many times, and then you turn

00:08:22.520 --> 00:08:23.290
over the last one
you're counting.

00:08:23.290 --> 00:08:24.230
So I'll show you very quickly.

